ComicInfo.Summary:
Trapped in the deadly and oppressive steampunk world of Oz, all hope seems lost for Skye Mathers. But, unbeknownst to her, across the many universes that separate her from home, Skye's allies are working on a way to get her back. Can Shang, Samantha and Allexa-- along with some questionable help from Baba Yaga-- succeed in bringing Skye home? Don’t miss this intense next issue in the Grimm Universe’s ever-expanding saga!
